          "text": "Solid concrete panels:\n\nType: {{panelType}}\nThickness: {{thk}} mm\nConcrete: min {{concCl}}\nRebar: min {{rebar}} kg/m²\nExt: {{extFin}}, Int: {{intFin}}\nAnchors: {{anchor}}\n\nConfirm: fire resistance (EI), weight/m², max dims, DoP/CE.\nSTM reserves the right to reject non-compliant alternatives.",
